{"tid":1054850,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"比起香港醫療制度崩潰 香港教育制度已經崩潰左好耐","createTime":"2019-03-10T06:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-10T17:43:51.000Z","uid":128093,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"57e66d00178c5e43ba06e54e8e7213d0b94ada9a","tid":1054850,"uid":128093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:50:21.000Z","msg":"教師工作沉重<br />\n而家正常老師一個禮拜30堂<br />\n根本無時間備課<br />\n搞到教唔好 學生又學唔好<br />\n最後人人都去補習<br />\n<br />\n有意投入教育事業既人大把<br />\n但政府唔肯比錢請多d人<br />\n其實教補習既人一半入翻傳統教育制度<br />\n所提供比學生既教育已經高質好多<br />\n年年大把人想讀pgde做老師<br />\n取錄率又低<br />\n教協而家仲話緊+0.3<br />\n其實+1都唔過分啦 +1都仲係30堂變20堂咋<br />\n<br />\n醫療制度又係咁 d人寧願投入私人市場都唔入公家<br />\n教育制度又係咁<br />\n香港特首真係好心搞搞佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1070b8d2fcaabaea9807553887dc95564e474dae","tid":1054850,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:53:21.000Z","msg":"1/3學校可以cut得<br />\n<br />\n大比學校一級得2班20個學生<br />\n<br />\n洗鬼咁多校長副校長"},{"pid":"8bb3b0b03f793119e29d6a6839a5cda840efd811","tid":1054850,"uid":71748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:54:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1/3學校可以cut得<br />\n<br />\n大<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">把</span></span></strong>學校一級得2班20個學生<br />\n<br />\n洗鬼咁多校長副校長</blockquote>"},{"pid":"18b2a1ef6cbbdd92c79a5735ff4cb87bd9111908","tid":1054850,"uid":76793,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T08:03:58.000Z","msg":"係咪又想加人工呀？"},{"pid":"c4cfafed7b28b53595fd78fbbca48d9176ed3d56","tid":1054850,"uid":175598,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T08:10:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c10cdb18487d8cf671df52d8e4491be28cf00ad1","tid":1054850,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c4cfafed7b28b53595fd78fbbca48d9176ed3d56","tid":1054850,"uid":175598,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T08:10:53.000Z","msg":"此回